msgstr "基本语法"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:8
msgid ""
"CSS style description can be viewed as a series of key-value pairs,each of "
"which describes a particular style, such as the width and height of a "
"component."
msgstr ""
"CSS样式的描述可以看作是一系列的键-值对，每个代表了一种特定的样式，如一个组件"
"的宽度和高度。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:12
msgid "``` width: 400; height: 50; ...  ```"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:14
msgid ""
"The format of key-value pairs is `prop-name: prop-value;`. The key name is "
"`prop-name`, the value name is `prop-value`.  Usually,the key name and the "
"value name follow Horizontal connection nomenclature, the value may be a "
"number(the default units is px); The key and the value must be separated by "
"`:`, between each key-value pairs must be separated by `;`."
msgstr ""
"键值对的格式如`prop-name: prop-value;` 。 键名为 ``prop-name``，值为 ``prop-"
"value``.  通常，键/值的名称都通过水平线相连 ，值可以是一个数字 ( 默认单位为 "
"px); 键-值用 `:` 隔开, 不同键值对以 `;` 区隔。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:16
msgid "The style description will appear on a weex page in two formats:"
msgstr "weex 页面中样式有两种写法："

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:19
msgid "Style attribute of `<template>` label"
msgstr "`<template>`标签的 style 属性"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:19
msgid "Stylesheets of `<style>` label"
msgstr "`<style>` 中的样式表"

#. type: Title ###
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "style attribute"
msgstr "style 属性"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:23
msgid "The style written in the style label, for example:"
msgstr "标签上的内联 style ，例如："

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:31
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <container style=\"width: 400; height: 50;\">\n"
"    ...\n"
"  </container>\n"
"</template>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is said that the width and height of `<container>` label is 400 pixels and 50 pixels respectively.\n"
msgstr "这是说，`<container>`标签的宽度和高度分别为400像素和50像素。\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "the `<style>` tag"
msgstr "`<style>` 标签"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:37
msgid "For example:"
msgstr "例如："

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:45
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```\n"
"<style>\n"
"  .wrapper {width: 600;}\n"
"  .title {width: 400; height: 50;}\n"
"  .highlight {color: #ff0000;}\n"
"</style>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:47
msgid ""
"The stylesheets contain multiple style rules, each style rule has only one "
"class which is contained by its style selector, a pair of curly braces `{...}"
"`, and the styles of the curly braces. For example:"
msgstr ""
"样式表包含多个样式规则，每个样式规则只有一个class样式选择器，一对花括号 "
"`{...}` 。例如："

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:51
msgid "``` .title {width: 400; height: 50;} ```"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:53
msgid "The above is a rule."
msgstr "以上是一个规则。 "

#. type: Title ###
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:54
#, no-wrap
msgid "Class attribute"
msgstr "class 属性"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:57
#, no-wrap
msgid "The selectors of `<style>` label are matched with the class attribute of `<template>` label, we should use spaces to separate the class names. For example:\n"
msgstr "`<style>` 中的 class样式选择器 匹配 `<template>` 中的 class 属性，多个类名之间用空格分开。例如： \n"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:71
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <container class=\"wrapper\">\n"
"    <text class=\"title\">...</text>\n"
"    <text class=\"title highlight\">...</text>\n"
"  </container>\n"
"</template>\n"
"<style>\n"
"  .wrapper {width: 600;}\n"
"  .title {width: 400; height: 50;}\n"
"  .highlight {color: #ff0000;}\n"
"</style>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:73
msgid ""
"It means that the width of the outermost container is 600px, The inside of "
"the two title text is 400 pixels high 50 pixels wide, the second piece of "
"text is red."
msgstr ""
"这意味着，最外层的容器的宽度为600px，这两个标题文本里面是400像素高，50像素"
"宽，正文第二段是红色的。 "

#. type: Title ###
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "笔记 ???"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:81
msgid ""
"In order to simplify the page design and the complete underlying "
"implementation, the width of our default screen is unified to 750 pixels, "
"different screens should be scaled with corresponding ratio."
msgstr ""
"为了简化页面设计和底层实现，我们默认屏幕的宽度统一为750个像素，不同尺寸的屏幕"
"应按比例缩小与相应的比例。 "

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:81
msgid ""
"The CSS standard may support a lot of selectors, but now weex only support "
"single-class selector."
msgstr "CSS标准可以支持很多的选择器，但现在weex只支持单个class选择器。"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:81
msgid ""
"The CSS standard can support many types of length units, but now weex only "
"support pixel, and the `px` unit could be ignored, you can write number "
"directly. More details can be found in [commmon styles](../references/common-"
"style.md)."
msgstr ""
"CSS标准可以支持多种类型的长度单位，但现在weex只支持像素，`px` 单位可以忽略，"
"你可以直接写数字。更多的细节可以 [参见 通用样式](../references/common-style."
"md)。 "

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:81
msgid ""
"The styles of Weex cannot be inherited to children elements, this is "
"different to the CSS standard, such as `color` and `font-size`."
msgstr ""
"weex的子元素不能继承样式，这与CSS标准不同，如`color`` and ``font-size`。 "

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:81
msgid ""
"The CSS standard contains a lot of styles, but weex only sopport few styles "
"which include layouts such as box model, flexbox, positions. And styles "
"include `font-size`, `color`, etc."
msgstr ""
"CSS标准包含了很多样式，但weex只支持有限的样式，比如 盒模型，flexbox，"
"positions。以及 `font-size``, ``color`，等。"

#. type: Title ##
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "With Data-binding"
msgstr "数据绑定"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:85
msgid ""
"Page [data](./data-binding.md) can be bound in `style` and `class` "
"attribute. For example:"
msgstr ""
"[数据绑定](./data-binding.md) 能绑定在`style` 与 `class` 属性上。例如："

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/style-n-class.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <container>\n"
"    <text style=\"font-size: {{fontSize}};\">Alibaba</text>\n"
"    <text class=\"large {{textClass}}\">Weex Team</text>\n"
"  </container>\n"
"</template>\n"
"<style>\n"
"  .large {font-size: 32;}\n"
"  .highlight {color: #ff0000;}\n"
"</style>\n"
"<script>\n"
"  module.exports = {\n"
"    data: {\n"
"      fontSize: 32,\n"
"      textClass: 'highlight'\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"</script>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

